env PAGER=cat man timing_report_constraint_rise_fall_clock_period_ check
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report...k_period_check(25.10)    timing_report...k_period_check(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_constraint_rise_fall_clock_period_check

Syntax
       timing_report_constraint_rise_fall_clock_period_check

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting of rise-to-rise and fall-to-fall clock_period checks
       separately for the report_constraint command.

       When set to false, the software reports the rise-to-rise  and  fall-to-
       fall  clock  period checks under the same table in the report. With the
       false setting, when the report_constraint -check_type clock_period  op-
       tion  is  specified, the software reports violations that are the worst
       amongst all the rise-fall transitions for each point.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

